        "prompt": "Use case: photorealistic-natural\nAsset type: Morphous Lotus transparent motif chroma-key source\nPrimary request: Create only a richly colored pink lotus bloom motif for a design-system catalog, isolated as one complete subject on a removable chroma-key background.\nSubject: A graceful pink lotus flower with layered translucent petals in visible lotus pink, rose-pink tips, warm cream petal bases, golden center hints, jade-green lotus leaves, short pond stem, subtle pale aqua water reflections on petal edges, and mud-brown natural grounding details. Botanical accuracy, crisp cutout edges, serene still pond identity. The petals must be colorful pink, not gray, not monochrome, not white.\nComposition/framing: centered complete cutout with generous padding; include bloom, leaf, and stem without cropping. Clean studio lighting, no cast shadow.\nChroma-key background: perfectly flat solid #0000ff blue background for removal. The background must be one uniform color with no shadows, gradients, texture, reflections, floor plane, or lighting variation. Do not use pure #0000ff anywhere in the subject.\nConstraints: no rose, no lily bouquet, no vase, no spa stones, no candle, no landscape, no text, no watermark, no loose petals, no second plant species, no grayscale petals."
