        "asset": "/systems/morphous-magnolia/motif.png",
        "prompt": "Use case: photorealistic-natural\nAsset type: Morphous Magnolia transparent motif chroma-key source\nPrimary request: Create only a southern magnolia blossom botanical motif for a design-system catalog, isolated as a single complete subject on a removable chroma-key background.\nSubject: A large cream magnolia blossom with thick waxy petals, gentle blush-brown petal shadows, glossy deep green oval leaves, warm brown branch segment, and sturdy sepals. Botanical accuracy, crisp subject edges, sculptural garden flower identity, no water lily, no lotus.\nComposition/framing: centered complete cutout with generous padding; include blossom, leaves, and short branch without cropping. Clean studio lighting, no cast shadow.\nChroma-key background: perfectly flat solid #ff00ff background for removal. The background must be one uniform color with no shadows, gradients, texture, reflections, floor plane, or lighting variation. Do not use #ff00ff anywhere in the subject.\nConstraints: no floating lily pad, no lotus pod, no dahlia petals, no bouquet, no vase, no full garden scene, no hand, no text, no watermark."
