        "asset": "/systems/morphous-magnolia/design-system-light.png",
        "prompt": "Use case: ui-mockup\nAsset type: Morphous Magnolia light-mode design-system board\nPrimary request: Generate one comprehensive light-mode design-system board for a Morphous theme named \"Morphous Magnolia\", derived from the visible southern magnolia blossom cutout. This board is a source reference for implementing a shadcn/tweakcn-compatible elegant portfolio system.\nCanvas: wide 16:9 high-resolution board, clean professional UI design-system presentation.\nRequired visible sections: Morphous Magnolia, Magnolia Blossom, Palette, Typography, Components, Navigation, Dashboard, Forms, Table, Command/Search, Status, Texture, Radius, Spacing, Shadow, Tokens.\nReference use: Extract the palette and interaction language from cream waxy petals, blush shadows, glossy leaf green, warm brown branch, garden ivory surfaces, and sepal umber depth. The board must read as magnolia, not water lily, lotus, dahlia, or generic luxury beige.\nTypography: English product UI examples with Japanese typography guidance; labels such as Geist, Noto Sans JP, Display, Body, Label, Numbers, 日本語 UI. Keep text short and legible.\nUI coverage: buttons, inputs, select, textarea, checkbox, radio, switch, tabs, badges, alerts, cards, table rows, search command palette, gallery navigation, portfolio dashboard metric cards, image list table, forms, empty/loading/error states, spacing, radius, border, shadow, texture samples, simple icons.\nStyle: premium shadcn/tweakcn-style product design system, precise grid, 8px card radius, petal-cream surfaces, magnolia-leaf primary actions, blush accent chips, branch-brown borders, layered petal cards, glossy leaf status accents, subtle wax-petal texture.\nConstraints: no lily pad, no lotus pod, no dahlia rosette, no generic purple/blue gradients, no unrelated saturated colors, no beige-only palette, no watermark, no random brand names, no misspelling of \"Morphous Magnolia\", no tiny unreadable paragraphs."
